name: Blue Floral Print on Navy Tee
description:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

All tees are made from American Apparel 2001 Model Fine Jersey. The product is all manufactured sweatshop free in the USA.  

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

•	Made in Austin, TX
•	High Quality 100% Ring-Spun Cotton 
•	Custom Woven Label placed on the bottom of shirt. 
•	Fits true to size. 
•	Made to Order Custom Pocket (each product is unique!)
•	Men's/Unisex 
•	Model is 5'9" wearing Size Small

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Wash Instructions:

•	Wash in cold water with like colors
•	Tumble dry low or air dry
•	Pocket is iron safe
•	Label with logo is NOT iron safe
